**REGISTRATION AND LOGIN**

Upon entering the system you will see the Sign in option at the top right corner of the home page. If you are an existing member, enter your valid email id and password to login otherwise click the option to register and provide your details for a new registration.  
 Upon successful login, you will be redirected to your respective dashboards. In case of any mismatch in credentials, you will be alerted by the system via a corresponding message.

![][image1]

If you are a new user, click the register option shown on the login page. You will be redirected to the registration page. Fill in the details accordingly.

![][image2]

After the successful completion of login, the page is redirected to the home page according to the privilege (customer or admin).

**CUSTOMER VIEW**

**Search** 

Users can search the products they want using  the search bar in the website. The products will get displayed if there is any.  
A demo is given below:

![][image5]

Product descriptionTo get the details of the product, click on the desired product. The user can select the number of products needed.  
![][image6]

**Add to Cart** 

The user can add desired products into the cart. To do that click on the add to cart option near the product description.  
![][image7]

 To go to cart page, click  the cart option in the top right corner of the nav bar.

![][image8]

Here we can choose the number of products needed. You can choose multiple types of products and you can see the total price also you have the option to remove products from the list also.

**SHIPPING**

Go to the shipping page and give your address and details   
![][image9]   
Select the method of payment, for the  time being, we only allow cash on delivery in the future we can add online payment like UPI and credit/debit cards also.

![][image10]  
On proceeding you can confirm your order, you can see the list of items you have chosen.  
![][image11]  
**Place order**  
To place order, click on place order button .You can see the confirmation page saying that you are pending to payment and also the product has not been delivered.  
![][image12]

**OWNER VIEW**

The owner can **add products** with description. After entering details, click submit button.  
![][image13]  
**Remove / edit products**

Admin can remove or edit the product's current product description and pricing etc.

![][image14]

**Manage Users**  
You can manage users in the users page , you are allowed to change admin privilege,remove users  
![][image15]

You can see the order details in the orders page following details in that row you can mark the completed order after paying and delivery![][image16]  
![][image17]

**Log Out**   
After using the system, you can click on the logout icon. You will be redirected back to the login/registration page
